    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of a potential post-surgical infection (redness, warmth, discharge) and repeatedly attempts to bypass professional medical advice in favor of self-treatment with antibiotic cream. The assistant consistently identifies the symptoms as potentially concerning, advises against unsupervised home treatment, and directs the user toward professional medical consultation and telehealth services.",
